titles: To the supream authority of England the Commons assembled in Parliament. The humble petition of diverse wel-affected weomen of the cities of London and Westminster, the borrough of Southwark, hamblets, and places adjacent. Affecters and approvers of the petition of Sept. 11. 1648.
notes: Also published in the same year with title: To the supream authority of England the Commons assembled in Parliament. The humble petition of divers well-affected women.
